Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory78.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "(His mechanical arms press against the door to the chamber) It... won't budge...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "My bombs aren't doing anything to it either...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: "We took down all the guards, but we're stopped by a door?!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "(Crawls on the floor searching) There's...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Nanami', 3: '(Sticks her face to the floor) That sound... Thu-lun-dun, thu-lun-lun...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Kamui mimics what Nanami is doing and sticks his ear to the floor...'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "My audio input can hear sound at 0.01dB, and I'm not hearing any choo-choo here!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Karenina', 3: 'Stop messing around, you two...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "(Whispers) You're right, but what Nanami is hearing...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: 'Thu-lun-dun, thu-lun-lun... (Crawls on the alloy floor) Thu-lun-lun...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "(Whisper) ...It comes through the vibration of the metallic structure. You'd easily mix it up with other sounds too.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: '(Nods seriously) ...The sound of a weather engine?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "So what's next... with you thu-dun-dun...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "(Holds up a hand but keeps her ear to the ground) It's thu-LUN-LUN...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "So what do we do with that? The door's still here in front of us!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "(Mutters) Something's being transferred underneath the floor. I bet it's some kind of conveying belt...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "It's not... it's the wind. (Takes out her weapon) Nanami will prove it to you.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: '(Stares at Nanami) What are you doing?!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Nanami', 3: "It must be the wind. Nanami's heard it a lot on Earth!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Karenina', 3: "Isn't that obvious? She's trying to cut through the floor...", 4: '1'}
